---
title: Chipotle Pulled Chicken Sandwiches with Carrot Apple Slaw
description: Delicious pulled chicken sandwiches in just 20 minutes? Yep! We’re making it happen. These bad boys in buns contain precooked pulled chicken—all you have to do is heat it in a pan and you’re at tender, juicy bliss. Although that meat isn’t the only star of the show. To keep things fresh, there’s also an apple carrot slaw, plus a spiced chipotle sour cream for a bit of smoky intrigue.
